I absolutely love this purchase and it is the first pair of headphones that I can comfotable take around with me. I can either put it in the protective case that comes with it or hang it around my neck. I sometimes forget that I even have headphones around my neck because of how light it is. (You know that feeling of light but heavy so you know it is good quality).		
		
