"B. J. Colorafi,""Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2024"",""I purchased the Sony WH-1000XM4 headphones from Amazon in June of 2024. I was in the market for high quality headphones to replace my Beats Studio Pro headphones which I found to be slightly pitchy at higher volumes. I also considered the Sony WH-1000XM5, but they slightly above my price range."		
		
